snippet.title: LMK Tech Demo E3 2000 Trailer
snippet.description: E3 2000 tech demo of The Lady, Tha Mage, & The Knight (LMK), an unfinished isometric RPG, is shown here in this trailer and was released in the GOG's Divinity campaign.
